TitMainTitle: Men, including one wearing army uniform, and women including one on right wearing dark beret and jacket with plaid front, seated in banquette with bottles and glasses, in bar with sponge painted block walls, vents over tables, and broadsides reading "Colored Union Labors Club, Inital Post-War Dance...Union Hall...Henry Foster and his Krazy Kats...", possibly in Crawford Grill No. 2
